OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few bright or sunny spells
OL,6,Fotherwise rather cloudy. Mainly dry
OL,7,Fwith just a few scattered showers.
OL,8,FRather cold but winds will be light
OL,9,Fand variable.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mainly dry but cloudy
OL,12,Fevening then turning increasingly
OL,13,Fclear during the night. Quite a cold
OL,14,Fnight with light to moderate
OL,15,Fnortheasterly breezes.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA mainly dry day with some
OL,18,Fgood spells of sunshine. Perhaps the
OL,19,Fodd shower in the northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
