OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,6,Fmainly dry with some sunny spells.
OL,7,FCloudier with a few showers on Monday.
OL,8,FBreezy on Tuesday with sunny intervals
OL,9,Fand showers.
